545
00:30:05,299 --> 00:30:06,471
Where is she?

546
00:30:06,732 --> 00:30:08,917
It doesn't matter; no one's gonna kill her.

547
00:30:09,005 --> 00:30:10,198
You have my word.

548
00:30:10,674 --> 00:30:12,324
Cross my heart and hope to...

549
