745
00:41:08,388 --> 00:41:09,712
You don't understand.

746
00:41:10,517 --> 00:41:12,196
I'm not going to let this happen.

747
00:41:12,396 --> 00:41:15,543
No, you're the one who doesn't understand.

748
00:41:16,138 --> 00:41:17,720
